        &lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This application showcases how Radius can use a user-managed Azure SQL Database.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;resource-format&#34;&gt;Resource format&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;nav nav-tabs&#34; id=&#34;tabs-0&#34; role=&#34;tablist&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;nav-item&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;nav-link active&#34;
