    <item>
      <title>Reference: MongoDB database</title>
      <link>https://docs.radapp.io/reference/resource-schema/databases/mongodb/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://docs.radapp.io/reference/resource-schema/databases/mongodb/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;mongodb.com/MongoDatabase&lt;/code&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.radapp.io/guides/author-apps/portable-resources/&#34;&gt;resource&lt;/a&gt; represents a Mongo database.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;resource-format&#34;&gt;Resource format&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;nav nav-tabs&#34; id=&#34;tabs-1&#34; role=&#34;tablist&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;nav-item&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;nav-link active&#34;
